title: StartGraf
body:
Good evening, my lady. 
[[Good evening, Graf Von Azabu.|GrafGood01]]
[[Good evening, Sir.|GrafNeutral01]]
[[Good evening, Wentzel.|GrafBad01]]

title: GrafGood01
body:
You may call me Wentzel, my lady. 
[[You may call me anytime, my lord.|GrafGood02]]
[[Thank you, my lord. |GrafNeutral02]]
[[I prefer Graf Von Azabu|GrafBad02]]

title: GrafBad01
body:
That's Graf Von Azabu for you. 
[[Pardon, my lord. I meant no disrespect.|GrafNeutral02]]
[[That's Graf Von Azabu for you MY LADY!|GrafBad02]]
[[Fine by me, Graf Von Azabu.|GrafBad02]]

title: GrafNeutral01
body:
You may call me Wentzel, my lady. 
[[Thank you, Wentzel. I'm honored.|GrafGood02]]
[[Thank you, my lord.|GrafNeutral02]]
[[I prefer Graf von Azabu.|GrafBad02]]

title: GrafGood02
body:
Are you enjoying the party, my lady? 
[[Yes, especially present company.|GrafGoodEnding]]
[[Yes, thank you for the invitation, Wentzel. |GrafGoodEnding]]
[[Yes, especially the cherry blossoms, my lord.|GrafNeutralEnding]]

title: GrafNeutral02
body:
Are you enjoying the party, my lady? 
[[Yes, especially present company.|GrafNeutralEnding]]
[[Yes, thank you for the invitation, Wentzel.|GrafNeutralEnding]]
[[Yes, especially the cherry blossoms, my lord.|GrafBadEnding]]

title: GrafBad02
body:
You have quite the mouth on you.
[[You could say I have a silver tongue.|GrafNeutralending]]
[[You'll like it once we're married, Graf.|GrafBadEnding]]
[[I bet you like that about me though.|GrafBadEnding]]

title: GrafGoodEnding
body: Well, I'm charmed. I hope you enjoy your stay.
